 Hits 40 Million YouTube Subscribers, Adds 18,000+ Subs Per Day|work=[[Tubefilter]]|date=26 October 2015|accessdate=15 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"background:#b53e3a;\" align=\"center\" colspan=\"5\"| <b style=\"color: #FFFFFF;\">2016 </b>\n|-\n| \"LEVEL 7 {{pipe}} I'M NOT CRAZY (OUTLAST IRL GAMEPLAY)\"\n| align=\"right\" | 10 February 2016\n| PewDiePie encounters situations and sets inspired by the video game ''[[Outlast (video game)|Outlast]]''.<br/>This video is the 7th episode of the [[YouTube Premium|YouTube Red]] series ''[[Scare PewDiePie]]''.\n| align=\"center\" | <ref group =\"\u2021\" name=scarePDP7/>\n| align=\"center\" | <ref name=Hernandez2016/>\n|-\n| \"OLD VS. NEW PEWDIEPIE! (Fridays With PewDiePie - Part 111)\"\n| align=\"right\" | 24 April 2016\n| PewDiePie views his older videos and compares them to his newer video style.<br/>This video is the 111th episode of PewDiePie's ''Fridays with PewDiePie'' series.\n| align=\"center\" | <ref group =\"\u2021\" name=\"fridayswithPDP111\">{{Cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X4dAPKYPhDQ |title=OLD VS. NEW PEWDIEPIE! (Fridays With PewDiePie - Part 111) |date=24 April 2016 |publisher=[[YouTube]] |access-date=6 January 2019 |work=[[PewDiePie]]}}</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | <ref name=\"Campbell2016\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.polygon.com/2016/4/25/11504178/pewdiepie-offensive-jokes |title=PewDiePie distances himself from offensive jokes, says he's grown up |last=Campbell |first=Colin |date=25 April 2016 |work=[[Polygon (website)|Polygon]] |access-date=6 January 2019}}</ref> \n|-\n| \"I'M LOSING SUBS!!!!\"\n| align=\"right\" | 29 June 2016\n| PewDiePie discusses YouTube's platform-wide subscriber purge.\n| align=\"center\" | <ref group =\"\u2021\" name=\"losingsubs\">{{Cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=26qVo4kNMSU|title=I'M LOSING SUBS!!!!|date=29 June 2016 |publisher=[[YouTube]] |access-date=22 April 2020 |work=[[PewDiePie]]}}</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | <ref name=\"Spangle