 Respond Well (So Far) |last=Brouwer |first=Bree |date=13 October 2014 |work=[[Tubefilter]] |access-date=5 January 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| \"FUNNY MONTAGE #3\"\n| align=\"right\" | 25 October 2014\n| A compilation of PewDiePie's Let's Play videos.\n| align=\"center\" | <ref group =\"\u2021\" name=\"funnymontage3\">{{Cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nxQO53J2_OQ |title=FUNNY MONTAGE #3 |date=25 October 2014 |publisher=[[YouTube]] |access-date=3 January 2019 |work=[[PewDiePie]]}}</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | <ref name=Mamiit2015/>\n|-\n| \"31,970,288 Subscribers!!!!\"\n| align=\"right\" | 5 November 2014\n| PewDiePie expresses his appreciation of his viewers and mentions how disabling comments made him feel happier.\n| align=\"center\" | <ref group =\"\u2021\" name=\"31,subscribers\">{{Cite AV media |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Og02p2Y4fRQ |title=31,970,288 Subscribers!!!! |date=5 November 2014 |publisher=[[YouTube]] |access-date=5 January 2019 |work=[[PewDiePie]]}}</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | <ref name=\"Kuchera2014\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.polygon.com/2014/11/5/7163931/pewdiepie-youtube-comments-revisit |title=Turning off comments made YouTube's biggest star happier |last=Kuchera |first=Ben |date=5 November 2014 |work=[[Polygon (website)|Polygon]] |access-date=5 January 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| \"FIVE NIGHTS AT FREDDY'S 2 - Walkthrough / Playthrough / Gameplay - (NIGHT 1)\"\n| align=\"right\" | 11 November 2014\n| PewDiePie commentates over ''[[Five Nights at Freddy's 2]]'' gameplay. \n| align=\"center\" | <ref group =\"\u2021\" name=fnaf2p1>{{cite AV media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gdQwEWgZX7M|title=FIVE NIGHTS AT FREDDY'S 2 - Walkthrough / Playthrough / Gameplay - (NIGHT 1)|work=[[PewDiePie]]|publisher=[[YouTube]]|date=11 November 2014|accessdate=15 April 2020}}</ref>\n| align=\"center\" | <ref name=Hernandez2014a>{{cite web|last=Hernandez|first=Patricia|url=https://kotaku.com/five-nights-at-freddys-2-as-told-by-steam-reviews-16579642